34:10.540 --> 34:14.940
I'm watching how price delivers around that order.

34:14.940 --> 34:19.640
Is it easily moving away from that order or is it lethargically moving away?

34:19.640 --> 34:22.140
Or is it completely running against it?

34:22.140 --> 34:28.540
That immediate feedback, that feedback loop that it gives you as a trader

34:28.540 --> 34:32.640
because you have something in there that's worth something, you're going to be

34:32.640 --> 34:38.240
